---
import Breadcrumbs from '@/components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import PageHead from '@/components/PageHead.astro'
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout class="max-w-3xl">
  <PageHead slot="head" title="About" />
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'About', icon: 'lucide:info' }]} />

  <section>
    <div class="min-w-full">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2 class="mt-0">about me</h2>
        <p>
          hey, i'm paris. i'm one of those people who can't stick to just one thing —
          give me a rabbit hole and i'll dive in headfirst. physics, coding, economics,
          random wikipedia articles at 2am... you get the idea.
        </p>
        <p>
          i started this blog because i wanted a place to put all the things i learn.
          partly to share, partly so i don't forget everything. turns out writing stuff
          down actually helps it stick.
        </p>
        <h2>what you'll find here</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>tutorials and guides when i figure something out</li>
          <li>projects i'm working on (or abandoning)</li>
          <li>random thoughts that probably should've stayed in my notes app</li>
          <li>stuff i find interesting and want to ramble about</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          if any of that sounds interesting, stick around. if not, no hard feelings.
        </p>
        <h2>get in touch</h2>
        <p>
          feel free to reach out if you want to chat about anything.
          you can find me on github or twitter — links are in the footer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
